arStrings.szText: Slayer's Retribution
The former cannibal Varyana seeks vengeance against her betrayers
Mercenary - Varyana

Varyana, one of the mercenaries of the Pale Hand, left a note at the Mercenary Den saying they were seeking revenge at the Temple of Rot. I've followed a trail of blood to a larder in front of the Temple of Rot. I should investigate the larder.
Investigate the Fetid Larder
Varyana is on a quest for vengeance against cannibals who wronged her. We must search the Dry Stepps for clues that will help us find the hidden feast hall of Grelkar the Craven, her first target.
Find Cannibals loyal to Grelkar
Varyana is on a quest for vengeance against cannibals who wronged her. We now travel to feast hall of her first target, Gralkar the Craven.
Travel to Grelkar's Feast Hall
Varyana is on a quest for vengeance against cannibals who wronged her. It is time to enter Grelkar's feast hall and put an end to him.
Kill Grelkar
Varyana is on a quest for vengeance against cannibals who wronged her. We need to enter Guulrahn and kill her final target: Zolmog.
Enter Guulrhan and kill Zolmog
I rescued Varyana who was chained and driven to madness within a cellar. Now that she has calmed down, I should speak with her.
Speak with Varyana outside the Fetid Larder
Varyana is on a quest for vengeance against cannibals who wronged her. We need to find boat to enter Guulrahn and kill her final target: Zolmog.
Find a boat to sneak into Guulrhan
Varyana is on a quest for vengeance against cannibals who wronged her. We must search the Dry Steps for clues that will help us find the hidden feast hall of Grelkar the Craven, her first target.
Kill the Herald of Grelkar
Obtain a clue that reveals Grelkar's location

Varyana, one of the mercenaries of the Pale Hand, left a note at the Mercenary Den saying they were seeking revenge at the Temple of Rot. A crude sign written in blood revealed that the mercenary was held captive. A trail of blood leads out of the Temple of Rot.
Find the Fetid Larder

Varyana, one of the mercenaries of the Pale Hand, left a note at the Mercenary Den saying they were seeking revenge at the Temple of Rot. I should read the bloody sign I found within the Temple of Rot, perhaps it is a clue.
Read the Blood-Scribed Sign
Varyana, one of the mercenaries of the Pale Hand, left a note at the Mercenary Den saying they were seeking revenge at the Temple of Rot. I should search the Temple of Rot for clues.
Search the Temple of Rot for Varyana
Varyana is on a quest for vengeance against cannibals who wronged her. It is time to enter Grelkar's feast hall and put an end to him.
Enter Grelkar's Feast Hall

Speak with Varyana
